	<dita:topic xmlns="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="UK14_Precedents_link-dpsi">
  <title>link with @dpsi <lnpid>id-UK14-30217</lnpid></title>
  <body>
    <section>
      <p>When <sourcexml>link</sourcexml> includes <sourcexml>@dpsi</sourcexml>, convert as follows: <ul>
          <li><sourcexml>link</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>ref:lnlink</targetxml>.</li>
          <li>The content of <sourcexml>link</sourcexml> becomes
            <targetxml>ref:marker</targetxml>.</li>
          <li>Create <targetxml>ref:locator</targetxml> and populate the attribute
              <targetxml>ref:locator/@anchoridref</targetxml> with the value of
              <sourcexml>link/@refpt</sourcexml>.</li>
          <li>Suppress <sourcexml>@dpsi</sourcexml> and <sourcexml>@alt-label</sourcexml>.</li>
        </ul>
      </p></section>
    <section><b><u>Exception:</u></b> Suppress <sourcexml>link</sourcexml> entirely if value of
        <sourcexml>@alt-label</sourcexml> is <sourcexml>"Drafting note"</sourcexml>, i.e.
        <sourcexml>@alt-label="Drafting note"</sourcexml>.</section>
    <section>
      <note><targetxml>ref:locator/@anchoridref</targetxml> that begins with a number must have an
        underscore added at start. Also apply other identifier data type format as used for
          <targetxml>xml:id</targetxml> and <targetxml>ref:anchor/@id</targetxml> (e.g. change colon
        to underscore).</note>
    </section>

    <pre>
        <b>EXAMPLE</b>
            
<b><i>Source XML</i></b>

&lt;text&gt;The provisions of paragraph &lt;link refpt="ukContentItem7747aa59-2bfe-474f-aa15-b82ebe69b23a"
        dpsi="0SH3" alt-label="para"&gt;8&lt;/link&gt; of this letter shall apply unless otherwise specified
    in the master agreement&lt;link refpt="ukContentItem6ddf9a1d-1f8c-4f2d-bb45-f44ed68ead34"
        dpsi="0SH3" alt-label="Drafting note"/&gt;.&lt;/text&gt;
 
<b><i>Target XML</i></b>

&lt;text&gt;The provisions of paragraph 
    &lt;ref:lnlink&gt;
        &lt;ref:marker&gt;8&lt;/ref:marker&gt;
        &lt;ref:locator anchoridref="ukContentItem7747aa59-2bfe-474f-aa15-b82ebe69b23a"/&gt;
    &lt;/ref:lnlink&gt; of this letter shall apply unless otherwise specified in the master agreement.&lt;/text&gt;

                </pre>

